    "It is also worth noting that γ opt attains lower BEP than γ subopt, particularly at high α regime.",
    "However, the gap between the exact and approximated BEP curves decreases as N increases.Fig. 4(c) illustrates how the Rician factor, K, influences the BEP performance.",
    "As foreseen, as K increases, which corresponds to a stronger LoS contribution, the BEP improves.",
    "However, the gap between exact and approximated curves grows larger as δ and K increase.",
    "For K = 0 (i.e., Rayleigh fading), the BEP is higher compared to the cases with Rician factors K = 3, 5 and 10."
